{
  "stem": "9156.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Julius too was Jewish, part of the ISK underground, was already hunted so that he couldn't anymore stay any night, that same night, the next night overnight.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He had to always stay somewhere else, but he did it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was a teacher.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I once asked him when I met him, again at that time-- I said, Julius, you are much nicer than you were when I knew you way back before the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I never forget when he said, 'I learned something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I learned that people need each other.' And he wrote some beautiful-- I have it in my book-- to his parents, you know, about how he has had to do what he had to do.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But, anyhow, Julius came, and he said, you go on a train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I want to be-- and bringing you to that train so that we know that you are really leaving the country, that you are on that train.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And, you know, again, I have to tell you that each time when I left, I left everything behind.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There isn't much you take with you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I have to say something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It's only last year that I was back in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I have been back in Berlin before, but under other circumstance.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "When I passed through the Potsdamer Platz, which is one of the major-- I suddenly remembered something I had never remembered before, and that is that there were the women with the violets, that sell violets, and Julius bought a bunch of violets and said something good has to be taken out of this country.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, all right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very quick.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I get into Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By train?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By train.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Now, in Czechoslovakia are people who have helped refugees.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Carlsbad.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
